  "detailed_description": "Be an iguana and save the world from evil.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Create your own adorable iguana with the charming character creator<br></li><li>Solve puzzles and get help from other iguanas to collect the 4 big keys<br></li><li>Collect precious valuables to spend on unique consumables and stat boosts<br></li><li>Defeat strong invaders with strategy and clever use of items</li></ul><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365560/extras/95d484fda50fd5a2ebb63469d2bea10a.webp?t=1682289144\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365560/extras/95d484fda50fd5a2ebb63469d2bea10a.poster.avif?t=1682289144\" class=\"bb_img\" width=112 height=129 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Arrow Keys</strong> - Move<br></li><li><strong>Space</strong> - Jump, Confirm, Use potion<br></li><li><strong>U</strong> - View potion supply<br></li><li><strong>Q</strong> - ???</li></ul>",
